divs: Sighting Detailsi was sitting out side and saw a flashing light in the sky and then it moved in a weird way like no air craft ive ever seen. when i first saw it before it moved i thought it was mars but then it moved so that took that out of the picture. i was in shock. i have been through ghoast hauntings and ive seen other weird stuff but nothing like this. but after that i watched it for about 4 days and it kept moving and then it just disappeared so i thought until 2 nights ago then it came back but this time there was 2 more like they were surrounding us.
